{"tid":1549132,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"18區遍地開花月餅會","createTime":"2019-09-07T08:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:27:47.000Z","uid":314105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29e55480157e042bc8428a3f605e912b6b0f3308","tid":1549132,"uid":314105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>僅此聲明</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">此活動不是圍爐取暖活動。請各位手足謹記此點。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有無諗過，點解建制派蛇齋餅粽攻陷老人家做票倉，我們不可以?<br />\n有見及此，我正式宣佈<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">月餅獻老人</span></span></strong>活動，正式啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>活動定位</strong><br />\n我們目的是借在月餅打開廢老缺口，開展大量大宣工作。所以第一目標係深藍老人家 ! 其餘深紅偽中立群眾為次要目標。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>概念</strong><br />\n準備一系列的月餅(當中部份印上五大訴求，缺一不可等口號)，在中秋節於各區派發，配合放映會派傳單燈會等活動，同時給廢老們瘋狂做文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>現時情況<br />\n</strong>已經連絡了沙田區，深水埗區，南區與觀塘區的手足安排下星期五整餅和派月餅。另有其他區正等待開花。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>目標</strong><br />\n18區遍地開花，全力用蛇齋餅粽，攻陷廢老!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我們正現全力招募各方面人才(無論你係地區搞手，整餅達人，定文宣手足(需要大量)等等。，都希望你們加入我地，反攻廢老。</strong><br />\n<br />\n有意手足請入channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FNSNKxVSSes7SZfs-V7i7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFNSNKxVSSes7SZfs-V7i7Q&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=f4cc7268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FNSNKxVSSes7SZfs-V7i7Q</a><br />\n<br />\n參考沒事兒巴打post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1512791/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1512791/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25gKuak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25gKuak.png&h=07971e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8ecC3R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8ecC3R.png&h=89107758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0318c65434d8de690a729150d3326d50ac13a433","tid":1549132,"uid":246762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"}]}